ribute to the promotion of sub-regional integration within the WAEMU region, and increased trade between Mali and Côte d’Ivoire. The Project’s specific objective is to improve traffic flow and reduce transport time and cost on the Bamako-San Pedro Corridor. The project impact area covers the regions of Worodougou and Bagoué in Côte d’Ivoire and Sikasso in Mali.